Gifted Gypsy
The Gifted Gypsy is a wandering mystic and performer with a genuine but
unpredictable psychic gift. Unlike trained psionics, their abilities manifest
spontaneously and are tied to intuition rather than discipline.

Gifted Gypsies choose from Rogue, Physical, Technical, and Lore skill
categories. They are culturally knowledgeable, persuasive, and surprisingly
perceptive. Their psychic gifts manifest as minor psionic powers that expand
with level.

Attribute requirements: ME 12, MA 12.
Starting equipment: Colorful travelling clothes, musical instrument or
performance props, personal radio, a concealed knife, one week of rations,
and a small cache of trade goods.
